      "role": "user",
      "content": "stretching wont really fix this though, it's a really sharp pain. i have some advil here, i usually take it for any kind of pain. the \"might be a problem\" part sounds kind of vague, do you actually think it's dangerous or just a little extra thinning? i just need the headache to stop so i can function.",
